@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fsvgay(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.20 - wp.abs(v2 + 0.80)) * v2)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v2 + 0.31)) + wp.abs(tmp))
    v1 = (0.72 + ((v1 + 1.00 + tmp + 0.77) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.25)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.08) * v2) - v1)
    data[tid] = v0
